snippet.title: Conquer Humanity - Gameplay Trailer - PC Steam
snippet.description:
Become the super villain in this brutal, isometric, fast paced bullet hell by a solo developer. Master your unlimited powers in combat, dismember civilians, cause mass destruction, defeat armed enemies and unique bosses. Be ready to Conquer Humanity!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2215060/Conquer_Humanity/
